t: Powerful Nutrition and MMG Consumer Brands Combine to Form Powerful Brands - BevNET.com
s: February 10, 2021 - High-protein snack maker Powerful Nutrition announced last week it has combined with consumer products investing platform MMG Consumer Brands to form Powerful Brands, a CPG holding company focused on launching and acquiring health and wellness companies.
